article_html: Stuart Heritage leans down over the royal cot and fills in Prince William and the Duchess of Cambridge's daughter on her very important family. He says not to worry about a lifetime of public service, because there are a few people ahead of the royal baby in line to the throne. So a life of pleasure awaits
